-single-the-mad-stone-3542568">Everything Everything 分享的末日新单曲“The Mad Stone”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
您现在可以使用怀旧的像素化“demaster”来玩“黑暗之魂” https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/you-can-now-play-dark-souls-with-a-nostalgic-pixelated-demaster-3542562?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=you-can-现在用怀旧像素化解大师来玩《黑暗之魂》Ryan Easby Fri, 17 Nov 2023 17:10:48 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsPCVideo Game Culture https://www.nme.com/?p=3542562 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Dark-Souls-Remaster.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="黑暗之魂重制版（来源：Bandai Namco）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Dark-Souls-Remaster.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Dark-Souls-Remaster-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Dark-Souls-Remaster-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Dark-Souls-Remaster-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Dark-Souls-Remaster-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Dark-Souls-Remaster-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该模组为游戏添加了一个新层</p><p>帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/you-can-now-play-dark-souls-with-a-nostalgic-pixelated-demaster-3542562">“你现在可以用怀旧的像素化“demaster”来玩“黑暗之魂””</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Dark-Souls-Remaster.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="黑暗之魂重制版（来源：Bandai Namco）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Dark-Souls-Remaster.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Dark-Souls-Remaster-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Dark-Souls-Remaster-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Dark-Souls-Remaster-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Dark-Souls-Remaster-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Dark-Souls-Remaster-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>如果您是旧款复古游戏的粉丝，那么新游戏<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/dark-souls"> </a><em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/dark-souls">《黑暗之魂》</a></em>模组已经满足您的需求。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/game-reviews/alan-wake-2-review-3526841">《心灵杀手 2》评论：不要沉迷于这部令人不安的恐怖惊悚片</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.nexusmods.com/darksoulsremastered/mods/647"><em>Pixel Souls: Demastered</em></a>是为<em>Dark Souls Remastered 创建的，</em>可在 Nexus Mods 上使用，并使用基于游戏原始纹理的像素艺术替换所有纹理。它还降低了游戏中模型的质量并替换了标题中的音乐和音效。</p><p>至于这个模组是如何制作的，创建者“thegreatgramcracker”说道：</p><p> “ Pixel Art纹理是使用我自己的自定义图像处理算法创建的，并使用magick.net库。它们是使用原始游戏纹理建造的，并在区域逐个区域和敌方基础上进行了较小的更正和个人调整，以便一切看起来都像我希望的那样。该mod的任何部分都没有使用AI。”</p><p> Mod的预告片展示了所有正在进行的作品，而熟悉的Vistas上的锅则呈现到<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/ps1">PlayStation 1式的</a>荣耀中。它还展示了新的较低音频质量配乐，这为Demaster增添了极大的浸入水平。 </p><figure id="attachment_3542576" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3542576" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3542576" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Dark-Souls-Remastered.jpg" alt="黑暗的灵魂重新制作（信用：Bandai Namco）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Dark-Souls-Remastered.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Dark-Souls-Remastered-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Dark-Souls-Remastered-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Dark-Souls-Remastered-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Dark-Souls-Remastered-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Dark-Souls-Remastered-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3542576" class="wp-caption-text">黑暗的灵魂重新制作（信用：Bandai Namco）</figcaption></figure><p>这并不是第一个获得粉丝制作Demake的FromSoftware游戏。 <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/bloodborne">Bloodborne</a>是</em>Fromsoftware的PS4独家标题，去年与<em>Bloodborne <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/bloodborne-psx-retro-style-demake-is-available-now-3150688">PSX</a></em>获得了“ Demaster”，而其创造者将在2024年1月31日与<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/ps1-style-racing-game-bloodborne-kart-gets-a-release-date-3528082"><em>Bloodborne Kart</em></a>进行跟进。</p><p>这个粉丝制作的赛车冠军将包括12名独立的赛车手，一个单人竞选活动，设置了16个不同的地图，本地拆分屏幕多人游戏以及与战斗模式，交叉中仍存在Boss Battles，以将额外的挑战添加到游戏。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/star-wars-knights-of-the-old-republic">《星球大战：旧共和国的骑士》</a></em> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/star-wars-knights-of-the-old-republic-remake-absent-from-publishers-latest-report-3542520">完全没有出版商的最新报告</a>，这加剧了有关该游戏陷入困境发展的未经证实的报告。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/you-can-now-play-dark-souls-with-a-nostalgic-pixelated-demaster-3542562">您现在可以用怀旧的像素化“ Demaster”播放“黑暗灵魂”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
